text:
黄少天：……就是恰好
柳非：怎么恰好才能恰好成这样？ 你们恰好在一家酒店开房？
黄少天：他恰好家里没人
黄少天：所以来我家过年
黄少天：大家都是队友嘛要互相帮助啊哈哈哈哈……
喻文州：我是来见家长的
柳非：？？？？？？
黄少天：队长？？？？？？
楚云秀：！！！！！！！
苏沐橙：？！？！？！？！？！
trans:
Huang Shaotian: ...It’s just a coincidence
Liu Fei: How is that a coincidence? You just happened to be in a hotel room?
Huang Shaotian: He just happened to be home alone
Huang Shaotian: So he came over to my place for Chinese New Year
Huang Shaotian: We're teammates, after all, gotta help each other out, hahaha..
Yu Wenzhou: I’m here to meet his parents
Liu Fei: What?
Huang Shaotian: Captain, waht?
Chu Yunxiu: Oh!
Su Mucheng: What?
